Installation

Firstly install djagno-utilities
pip install -U django-utilities
pip install -U django-dynamic-pages

Configuration
Add utilities and dynamic_pages to INSTALLED_APPS in settings.py before django.contrib.admin:

INSTALLED_APPS = (
    …
    'utilities',
    'dynamic_pages',
    'django.contrib.admin',
    …
)

next add 'dynamic_pages.middleware.UrlsReloadMiddleware' to MIDDLEWARE_CLASSES

and finally 


